data.description: *ASK AGENT ABOUT INCENTIVES ON THIS HOME! Captivating 4-bedroom home in Festival Foothills is the one you've been waiting for! Discover a spacious open floor plan enveloped w/neutral tile floor, soothing palette, recessed lighting, & multi-sliders leading to the back patio, providing a seamless indoor-outdoor living experience. The gorgeous chef's kitchen is a cook's delight outfitted w/contemporary white shaker cabinets, a pantry, quartz counters, SS appliances, wall oven, & an island w/a breakfast bar perfect for casual dining. Main retreat showcases an immaculate ensuite w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet. This beauty also has a large backyard w/a covered patio & plenty of potential for customizing according to your tastes, whether you envision a lush garden or a swimming pool.
